ities and challenges through it all the bank has grown and met these opportunities and challenges along with you our customers and other constituents we have remained vital to community development by offering competitive products and services for individuals and businesses that are helpful and meaningful to their success by understanding communities we have been able to make timely decisions for housing job creation small business development community support and other local economic needs we pursue the most prudent banking practices  we gather deposits and provide loans in the communities we serve we continually give volunteer time and funding to local nonprofit and charitable organizations and causes the bank was founded with the principle philosophy of providing safe secure and stable banking services while supporting its communities and providing value to its owners it strikes me that the banks founders would be proud of what we have accomplished to date and would look brightly towards the future as we do as a community bank the farmers national bank of emlentons directors officers and associates take great pride in serving our many loyal customers we hope you enjoy the website and encourage you to explore the site and visit one of our seventeen community banking offices on behalf of everyone here at the bank thank you for your patronage and continued support of our proud institution title caotreas company emclaire financial corp job details company size  mil to less than  mil  employee range  to less than  additional professional information on amanda l blauser see amanda l blausers linkedin profile amanda l blausers social network and potential email matches find out potential social network profiles and potential email usernamed for amanda l blauser amanda l blausers known social networks and potential email matches find all of amanda l blausers social network profiles get full report search social networks including facebook linkedin myspace google twitter